# SLPRA 样本/演示个体 (A-Box) —— 非规范 FIXTURE，勿当权威 T-Box
#
# 按设计规约「TTL 只存 T-Box（+ 枚举/参考个体）；事务性 A-Box 存 SQLite/Postgres」，
# 本文件从 slpra-integration.ttl 外移而来。它不在 OntologyEngine.MODULE_FILES 的加载
# 清单内，也不在 ontology/slpra/*.ttl 顶层 glob 范围（位于 fixtures/ 子目录），故不进
# 生产 T-Box 物化、不被现有测试自动加载；仅供演示/手动按需加载，或后续 seed 进 DB。
# 权威 T-Box 见 ../slpra-*.ttl；枚举/参考个体（如 RiskLevel）仍留在各自模块 TTL。

@prefix rdf:   <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix rdfs:  <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .
@prefix owl:   <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix xsd:   <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .
@prefix slpra-drug:  <https://ontology.pharma-gmp.cn/slpra/drug/> .
@prefix slpra-equip: <https://ontology.pharma-gmp.cn/slpra/equipment/> .
@prefix slpra-contam:<https://ontology.pharma-gmp.cn/slpra/contamination/> .
@prefix slpra-risk:  <https://ontology.pharma-gmp.cn/slpra/risk/> .
@prefix slpra-facil: <https://ontology.pharma-gmp.cn/slpra/facility/> .

# ============================================================
# Sample Facility Individuals (from user equipment table)
# ============================================================

# Production Areas
slpra-facil:GeneralArea_SouthPlatform_Lower a slpra-facil:GeneralArea ;
    rdfs:label "一般区南平台下"@zh .

slpra-facil:GeneralArea_NorthPlatform_Lower a slpra-facil:GeneralArea ;
    rdfs:label "一般区北平台下"@zh .

slpra-facil:CleanArea_PurificationRoom a slpra-facil:CleanArea ;
    rdfs:label "洁净区精制间"@zh .

slpra-facil:CleanArea_DryingRoom a slpra-facil:CleanArea ;
    rdfs:label "洁净区干燥间"@zh .

slpra-facil:GeneralArea_DryingRoom a slpra-facil:GeneralArea ;
    rdfs:label "一般区干燥间"@zh .

slpra-facil:GeneralArea_5F_South a slpra-facil:GeneralArea ;
    rdfs:label "五楼一般区南"@zh .

# ============================================================
# Sample Equipment Individuals (from user equipment table)
# ============================================================

# Centrifuges
slpra-equip:CT64201 a slpra-equip:Centrifuge ;
    slpra-equip:equipmentID "CT64201" ;
    slpra-equip:equipmentName "离心机"@zh ;
    slpra-equip:modelSpecification "800" ;
    slpra-equip:constructedOf [ a slpra-equip:SS304WithHALARCoating ] ;
    slpra-equip:isInCleanArea false ;
    slpra-equip:hasEquipmentRole [ a slpra-equip:SharedEquipmentRole ] .

slpra-equip:CT64202 a slpra-equip:Centrifuge ;
    slpra-equip:equipmentID "CT64202" ;
    slpra-equip:equipmentName "离心机"@zh ;
